snippet.textDisplay: not trying to hate but it's literally cheaper to go out and buy coffee every day than to make coffee at home with this stuff every day. And the amount of times it says "sustainable" or "eco-friendly" in this video and on the site is straight greenwashing. This is not sustainable or eco-friendly. It's single use packaging that goes to landfill because even though it's plant-based and technically biodegradable, it only decomposes under industrial conditions which barely even exist. I wanted to love this product but until there's something better from chamberlain coffee I won't be buying it.
